about that urn?

200
00:16:06,593 --> 00:16:11,124
Well, from what you told me,
they could be talismans.

201
00:16:11,125 --> 00:16:13,652
Look, I'm gonna go and see
Monsignor Brusca tomorrow morning.

202
00:16:13,653 --> 00:16:15,630
Maybe he can shed
some more light on it.

203
00:16:15,631 --> 00:16:17,994
