208
00:16:31,077 --> 00:16:34,000
Well, maybe, maybe not.

209
00:16:34,001 --> 00:16:36,376
<i>- Hmph.
- What? [Chuckles]</i>

210
00:16:36,377 --> 00:16:38,323
I was just-

211
00:16:38,324 --> 00:16:41,543
<i>What, you don't think there are forces
out there we don't understand?</i>

212
00:16:41,544 --> 00:16:44,463
